Title: Who Are You Now?
Writer: Charlie Adlard (based on the graphic novel), Frank Darabont (developed by), Robert Kirkman (based on the graphic novel), Tony Moore (based on the graphic novel)
Actors: Norman Reedus, Danai Gurira, Alanna Masterson, Josh McDermitt
Plot: The Survivors encounter unfamiliar faces outside the safety of their community's walls and must decide whether or not this new group can be trusted.
